    {
      "bookmarkId": "34880565_31_1978-1992",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "1978-1992",
      "markText": "爱的本质就是生命的相互依赖。",
      "totalCount": 850,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34880565&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=1978&rangeEnd=1992",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d733227072143c35d73e028?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=1978&rangeEnd=1992"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34880565_30_2545-2582",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "2545-2582",
      "markText": "人们总是按照自己的思维方式去解释世界，尽力把一切事物都和自己的理解力拉平。",
      "totalCount": 476,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34880565&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=2545&rangeEnd=2582",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d733227072143c35d73e028?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=2545&rangeEnd=2582"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34880565_30_7006-7084",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "7006-7084",
      "markText": "逢到下雨天气，矮男人打伞去上班时，可能由于习惯，仍旧半举着伞。这时，人们有种奇妙的感觉，觉得那伞下好像有长长一大块空间，空空的，世界上任什么东西也填补不上。",
      "totalCount": 448,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34880565&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=7006&rangeEnd=7084",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d733227072143c35d73e028?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=7006&rangeEnd=7084"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34880565_19_1113-1137",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "1113-1137",
      "markText": "“不！你应该保持这样，说不定哪天又时兴胖子了！”",
      "totalCount": 434,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34880565&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1113&rangeEnd=1137",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d733227072143c35d73e028?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1113&rangeEnd=1137"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34880565_2_177-238",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "177-238",
      "markText": "甭管水里的鱼多杂，他想要哪种鱼就专上哪种鱼；他还能钓完公鱼钓母鱼，一对对地往上钓。他钓的大鱼比他还沉，钓的小鱼比鱼钩还小。",
      "totalCount": 430,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34880565&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=177&rangeEnd=238",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d733227072143c35d73e028?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=177&rangeEnd=238"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34880565_11_1334-1345",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1334-1345",
      "markText": "可是他娘是怎么知道的？",
      "totalCount": 403,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34880565&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1334&rangeEnd=1345",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d733227072143c35d73e028?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1334&rangeEnd=1345"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34880565_3_1450-1501",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1450-1501",
      "markText": "到底骗人不对，还是诚实不对？不然为嘛几十年拿假酒骗人，却相安无事，都喝得挺美，可一旦认真起来反倒毁了？",
      "totalCount": 400,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34880565&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1450&rangeEnd=1501",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d733227072143c35d73e028?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1450&rangeEnd=1501"
    },
